* **Backup & Disaster Recovery (`backup_management`):** A centralized GUI orchestrating `Kopia` and `pgBackRest`[cite: 3104]. It doesn't just take backups; it executes automated "Restore Drills" to mathematically prove the integrity of your snapshots, and alerts your on-call SRE if backups run stale or anomaly sizes are detected[cite: 1996, 3104, 3602].

